description: This classic, Outer Parkside home shows pride of ownership and offers three bedrooms on one level and two full baths.  A large formal living room with fireplace and double-paned windows, spacious formal dining room, classic eat-in kitchen with good cabinet space and updated appliances.  Full bath on the main level with stall shower and separate tub.  Three generous bedrooms with nice hardwood floors.  The lower level offers two car parking with ample storage, a laundry area, and a permitted additional room and full bath.  Quaint garden with concrete patio awaiting your personal touches.  Interior and exterior recently painted, and hardwood floors throughout most of the home.  Wonderful location near Ocean Beach, Zoo, Lakeshore shopping, and Lake Merced, with easy access to public transportation.

description: MESMERIZING panoramas captivate the viewer from the moment they step into this sky-high home. A modern kitchen opens to the living space with floor to ceiling windows that welcome gorgeous natural light throughout the day. A wrap around deck offers outdoor space while amplifying views from Angel Island to the north, City Hall to the south, and gorgeous city panoramic views spread out in-between. Wide plank flooring, stainless appliances, new carpeting, and designer paint throughout offer a move-in ready home. Nestled between Hayes Valley, Lower Pacific Heights, Polk St and Fillmore, you'll find a plethora of neighborhood amenities awaiting you. In-unit laundry, 24-hr security, parking, storage, and guest parking complete this perfect urban package.

description: Panoramic Views, Parking Spaces, and your Personal Touch! 2077 Thomas Ave is a charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath home nestled in Silver Terrace. This 1944 gem has great character, beautiful hardwood floors and natural light streaming through four skylights.     Upstairs includes: 2-bedrooms; front bedroom has bay and city views; rear bedroom has mountain and neighborhood views; 1-bathroom; formal living room; updated eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops, stone tile floors, energy-saving, stainless steel appliances and wet bar. Great room opens onto an expansive deck with panoramic mountain views!     Downstairs includes: two finished storage spaces converted to 1-bedroom and living/media room, (or can be used as 2-bedrooms); tandem garage with washer-dryer hookups and space for 1-2 cars inside; 1-car parking outside. Large paved backyard has potential for expansion. Home has solar panels.

description:
Fantastic 2-bedroom, 1 bathroom, center atrium home located in the Outer Sunset District of San Francisco. Recently renovated with new interior and exterior paint, refinished hardwood flooring, a new roof, updated electrical, and canned lighting. The kitchen is brand new, and the property includes a 1-car garage with a bonus room and a full bath downstairs. Enjoy the newly painted deck and the lovely rear yard.
Conveniently located near schools, parks, churches and public transportation.

description: This stylishly updated home boasts 3 bedrooms, an office, & 2 baths.  Step through the front gate to a covered entryway, perfect for a shoe storage bench. Just inside there's a convenient coat closet. The first floor features a modern bathroom, side-by-side laundry closet, bedroom with 3 windows, huge hall storage closet & immaculate 2 car garage with a work bench. Your guests can park in the driveway without blocking the sidewalk. Upstairs you'll find 2 bedrooms, an updated bathroom, & 3 skylights that make the space bright even on gloomy days. The rear bedroom has an attached sunroom/office with a closet. The combination living/dining room has been opened to the kitchen with a countertop to accommodate bar seating. There's abundant cabinetry in the kitchen along with a suite of SS appliances. There are peekaboo ocean views from the kitchen window. The enormous backyard is a delightful combination of verdant greenery & low maintenance. The perimeter features a drip irrigation system, & the main lawn is faux. The patio can easily accommodate a large dining table, & under the pergola is a perfect place to relax. Landscape lighting & Edison lights make the backyard easy to use in the evening as well. We are close to many shopping, dining & transit options.84 Walk Score! Zero Pest!

description: Nested in the heart of the serene Outer Sunset neighborhood, this beautifully updated 2bed/1bath residence - w/ a bonus bed/room & bath of approx 230 sq.ft in the garage- offers the perfect blend of modern amenities & classic San Francisco charm.  The home's thoughtful layout features a newly remodeled kitchen & bath- w/ permits-showcasing contemporary & premium fixtures.  The large backyard offers an expansive patio area perfect for relaxation, family gatherings & entertainment. Abundant natural light graces every room that pours through the newly installed milgard dual pane windows in both upstairs bedrooms and dining area.  The location is unparalleled just a few blocks from the majestic Ocean Beach & w/ an array of local eateries, quaint cafes, unique shops and markets as well as with easy access to public transportation and to the heart of the city, offering the perfect opportunity to experience the tranquility of beach living while remaining connected to the vibrant SF city life!

description: Sophisticated living await you in this dramatic and designer-finished three-story Mediterranean home on Mt Olympus.  How cool will it be to tell people where you live.  With this timeless architectural and updated transitional style, you will find yourself in the perfect secret spot of San Francisco.  And being on Mt Olympus, obviously the views are heavenly (sorry I could not help myself).   But the enchantment doesn't stop at the cute name of the mountain top, it just begins.  2-Car Parking. Views. Designer Finishes. Move-In Ready. You have everything you will need to make this your perfect home in San Francisco.    One of the best features has to be the street-to-street lot with terraced garden.  The garden features English roses, boxwood borders and Camellias.  In the backyard, escape to an unparalleled oasis of beauty. Back inside, the home just feels warm and comfortable.  Notables for the house include custom stained glass, Quoizel lighting, Loewen Bay/Awning windows framing sweeping views, a chef's kitchen with Perrin & Rowe Rohl fixtures.  The primary bedroom boasts downtown panoramic views as only Zeus and Hera would have it.   Found only at the top of Mt Olympus will you truly find the pinnacle of San Francisco living.

description: Surrounded by trees and lush landscape, 678 Clarendon Avenue is a 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath, three level town home in a gated community situated between Forest Hill and Forest Knolls.  The main level consists of an open kitchen/dining area, half bath and large living room complete with fireplace, wet bar and private deck with views of rich greenery. The upper level offers two ensuite bedrooms and a laundry room. New carpet throughout upper level bedrooms, new luxury vinyl plank floors on main level, dual pane windows, and freshly painted throughout. Spacious 2-car garage with additional storage space. The Woods' HOA amenities include community social center offering a gym, sauna, deck, and event space. Close to hiking trails, shopping in West Portal and Irving Street corridor, Forest Hill MUNI, and easy freeway access.

description: With easy access to restaurants, shopping, parks, culture & entertainment, this Cathedral Hill mid-century modern condo has remodeled & refined elements that are harmonious with its Joseph Eichler pedigree & firmly planted in the 21st century. The large quartz island seats 4 comfortably & anchors the sleek stainless Kitchen outfitted with custom cabinets, glass backsplash and in-unit washer/dryer combo. The open Living Room & 3 Bedrooms feature floor-to-ceiling windows opening to a huge terrace, flooded with sunlight. One of the three Bedrooms is used as an urbane formal Dining Room, perfect for dinner parties. Down the hall, a deep storage closet is tucked behind a stylish barn door & the first of 2 Bathrooms features aquamarine glass tiles. The Primary Suite provides comfort and tranquility, with custom closet systems & a luxurious Bathroom.  This unit boasts one car independent garage parking. Do not miss this opportunity to own a legendary illustration of mid-century design.

description: Experience luxury in this fully renovated contemporary home in the desirable Sea Cliff neighborhood. With abundant natural light, an open floor plan, and high-end finishes, it's ideal for stylish entertaining and relaxation.    The grand entry foyer features a striking glass staircase, setting the tone for modern finishes. The formal living room showcases a sleek fireplace, and accordion doors open to a deck and landscaped backyard for seamless indoor-outdoor living.    The dazzling white kitchen is the heart of this home, with a large island and counter seating for four. It flows seamlessly into the dining room & casual living space, perfect for hosting guests.    Upstairs, discover the primary suite w/walk-in closet, 2 additional bedrooms, and a luxurious dual-sink bathroom w/ a soaking tub & shower. A large bedroom offers a living area for versatile use. The top floor, w/ vaulted ceilings and skylights, can be a home office, gym, media room, or guest suite, complete w/ a full bathroom.    The lower level provides bonus space perfect for storage, a gym, media area, etc. A detached 2-car garage and landscaped yd complete this exceptional property. Located in the sought-after Sea Cliff neighborhood, it is just steps to China Beach, Baker Beach, Lands End Trail & The Presidio.

description: The word "loft'' evokes sophistication, height, space and air, cultural icons and their parties, photography and creating art, as well as access provided by superlative urban locations close to everything. This is a loft where you can find inspiration and recharge between urban adventures. Dramatic floor to ceiling windows, a well-appointed kitchen, large living/dining space, twin catwalks on the mezzanine level provide a home office or gym and a huge open closet that makes your personal effects look like well-organized dcor. Stairs flow from mezzanine to a private open air pent room w/panoramic views and access to larger shared roof deck. The kitchen's traditional look compliments the herringbone oak floors, while the oversized black chandelier and wallpaper choices bring a modern style. W/parking and outdoor space, it has it all. Steps to Oracle Park, shopping, culinary landmarks, tech giants, and freeways, this is the perfect SF location for a primary residence or a pied a Terre.

description: Exquisite Edwardian home with views in the highly sought after Richmond District. The main unit features an expansive floor plan over two levels with high ceilings, ample natural light and abundant storage. The main level consists of formal entry with foyer, living room with remotely operated gas fireplace, updated kitchen with custom cabinetry, formal dining room, powder room, and a laundry room. The upper level consists of two spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. The luxury en-suite features soaking bathtub with jets, glass stall shower, direct deck access, and views of the surrounding area. Additional features include throughout include hardwood floors, dual pane windows by Milgard, custom wooden plantation shutters, iSpring water filtration system and a recirculation pump for instant hot water. The second unit features an open floor plan and high ceilings. It consists of one bedroom, one bath, separate entry and a dedicated laundry facility. A large backyard creates the private oasis ideal for family events or personal enjoyment alike.

description: Stylish 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom mid century modern condo located in the heart of the the vibrant Mission District. Easy access to some of San Francisco's trendiest dining, nightlife, and retail as well as BART, Muni, tech shuttles and the highway. Highlights include an updated kitchen and bathroom, spacious living room with wood burning fireplace, a light filled formal dining room, beautiful hardwood floors throughout, small deck space, and two private and spacious bedrooms in the rear that overlook a beautifully landscaped garden. This turnkey unit is situated in a well maintained 2 unit building with solar panels, dual paned windows, shared garden with outdoor furniture, low $200/mo HOA dues, large deeded storage space, and 1 car garage parking. Transparent Pricing! Don't Miss!

description: Maison au Pont, a contemporary masterpiece in San Francisco's coveted Marina District, offers the first resale opportunity of this 2020-completed gem. Situated quietly at the rear of the building overlooking a tranquil interior garden, this upgraded 1 Bed 1 Bath condo boasts exquisite wood flooring, marble and stone finishes, air conditioning, in-unit washer/dryer, private parking, and a secure bike room. The convenience of a discreet garage entrance on Divisadero, access to a rooftop deck with stunning city and bay views, a pet-friendly atmosphere with a dog washing station, and a secure lobby enhance the lifestyle. Embrace an A+ location with the Marina Green, Crissy Field, the Presidio, Fort Mason, and renowned dining and shopping on Chestnut and Union Streets just moments away, making Maison au Pont the epitome of contemporary Marina District living

description: Transparent Pricing. Modern remodeled top floor condominium in a 2-unit building. Features include hardwood floors, double pane windows, skylight and solar panels. Spacious living room with corner fireplace and large double pane windows. Period archways and formal dining room with custom lighting and French doors. Remodeled modern chef's kitchen with quartz counters, abundant cabinetry, hexagonal tile floors and a large skylight. Stainless appliances include a Samsung gas range with vent hood, Amana refrigerator, and a dishwasher. Off the kitchen is a mud room and stairs leading to the garage and garden. 2 spacious bedrooms overlook the garden. Remodeled bath with custom tilework, soaking tub and shower with glass enclosure. Contemporary vanity and modern lighting. Bath includes a full-size, front-loading washer and dryer. Lush shared rear landscaped garden and patio with furniture and heat lamp  1 car tandem parking. A+ location 99 Walk/Transit Score.

Sunny courtyard, elevator, secure gated entry + 1 car parking. Restaurants, MUNI, Safeway, Whole Foods all nearby & at your fingertips! description: Welcome to this captivating 3 bed/2 bath single-family home nestled in the sought-after Outer Sunset. Just 2 short blocks from the beach, this home offers the quintessential coastal lifestyle with the convenience of city living. The home has recently undergone a thoughtful transformation, combining its original charm with modern updates. Upon entering the main level, you're greeted by an abundance of natural light, accentuating the fresh paint & newly refinished hardwood floors. The heart of the home is the stunning new eat in kitchen, designed with both style and functionality in mind. Boasting sleek countertops, new appliances, ample storage, and space to accommodate a table for 6. Whether you're hosting dinner parties or enjoying quiet family meals, this kitchen will impress. Each spacious bedroom provides comfortable retreats for relaxation. There is an ensuite bedroom & full bathroom on the ground level with 2 additional bedrooms & second full bath on the main level. Outside, the expansive backyard offers a private sanctuary, perfect for outdoor entertaining. 1 block to public transportation w/ easy access to downtown. With its perfect blend of original charm and modern conveniences, this Outer Sunset gem is truly a rare find. Don't miss this opportunity to make it your own.

description: Introducing the final release of units at 950 Tennessee Street. Recently constructed in 2020, 950 Tennessee represents an opportunity to own in one of the most exciting neighborhoods in San Francisco: the Dogpatch. For the city dweller looking for a peaceful home with modern amenities, Unit #401 is a top floor 2 bed, 2 bath condo with two private outdoor spaces. Danish-inspired interiors invoke a sense of warmth with clean lines, quality materials, and beautiful fixtures throughout, including Domus & Domus cabinetry, Caesarstone counters, and Bosch and Bertazzoni appliances. Completing this home are wide-plank oak flooring, in-unit washer and dryer, A/C, and 1 car parking. Storage is also available for purchase - inquire for more details. 950 Tennessee residents enjoy amenities such as an attended lobby, rooftop lounge with panoramic city and bay views, landscaped courtyard, dog spa, and bike room. Enjoy local favorites such as Hard Knox Cafe, Wooly Pig, Ungrafted, Piccino, Bandit, and Marcella's all within a half block radius. Ideally located near Esprit Park, Chase Center, Pier 70, easy freeway and public transit access, and much more.

description: Introducing this stunning Sunset residence, cherished by many generations of the same family! Ideally situated just short blocks away from Noriega & Irving Street's vibrant restaurants and shops, Judah Street MUNI lines, public transit on both Noriega & 19th Avenue, Sunset Recreation Center, and Sunset Reservoir, this home offers unparalleled convenience. The top floor of this charming Marina-style home boasts a barrel front living room with an original fireplace and a spacious formal dining room seamlessly integrated with an open kitchen with large skylight. Two bedrooms in the back side by side, a full bath, and a large deck off the bedrooms complete this level. Interior stairway off the long hallway leads to the ground level accessing a two-car garage with an additional legal bedroom & bath added over the decades. Completing this level is a substantial laundry room & a second spacious deck accessed either through the laundry room or the bedroom. Additionally, a separate side entrance provides access to the ground floor level, offering versatile living options. Discover the epitome of Sunset living in this remarkable home!

description: Breathtaking, panoramic views of the city and bay from nearly every room coupled with a gorgeous and spacious interior make this the perfect place to call home. This 3-level townhome lives like a single-family home with ample closets, 2 car/ plus parking and generous rooms. The chef inspired kitchen features newer stainless appliances, custom tile, an additional eating area that all flows into the family/great room. The main level also enjoys a  bathroom, formal dining room with built in cabinets and a living room with a fireplace all creating an elegant space for relaxing and entertaining. The primary bedroom, in-suite bathroom and walk in closet allow for privacy and comfort on the top floor. Enjoy the convenience of a large laundry room, additional bonus room, 2 generous bedrooms, bathroom, and a beautiful patio all rounding out the lower level. An ideal location near Glen Canyon Park, Diamond Heights Center with easy access to transportation, shops and dining.

description: Nestled in this serene and sunny part of Potrero Hill, 814 Carolina is an elegant, fully detached Victorian cottage. This renovated home combines classic features with modern living. A captivating and lush courtyard welcomes you upon arrival that leads up to your front patio. Step inside and discover a sunny haven under 9-foot ceilings and designer LED lighting. The smart layout comfortably maximizes space to include a modern chef's kitchen with quartz counters, full-size stainless appliances, including an externally vented gas range. Next to the dining room, the living room is adorned with custom built-in bookcases atop radiant heat wood floors. The oversized spa-like bathroom features a deep soaking tub and shower. A quiet and private office pod in the back is ideal to work from home. Additionally, the large concrete basement, which served as a functioning potters' studio, is a versatile space for your creative endeavors and storage needs. Upgrades such as a combo tankless water heater boiler, 100 amps of power, in-unit laundry, enhance the home's functionality. This part of Carolina enjoys ample street parking, as it lacks bus lines and is not a direct throughway. With its meticulous use of space and handpicked features, 814 Carolina is truly a special happy place.

description: Reduced 100k! This elegant flat nestled in Alamo Square seamlessly marries timeless charm with contemporary comfort.  With high ceilings, original molding, medallions, pocket doors and redwood trim, this spacious condo is the perfect blend of old-world craftsmanship and modern sophistication. The living room beckons with large bay windows, tasteful period details, newer custom-built redwood shelving, and a restored gas fireplace.  There are 3 bedrooms, plus a home office with two built-in desks, a generous full bathroom with shower over tub, plus a separate powder room. Toward the back of the home, you'll find an updated kitchen and formal dining room with a charming decorative fireplace. Sliding doors in both rooms open to a small patio, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or an evening cocktail. Included with this unit is a full size W/D, one car PARKING with an EV charger and built-in storage.  There are solar panels exclusive to this unit.  With its timeless charm, modern amenities, and prime location near the cities most famous park, NoPa and Hayes Valley, this elegant home offers the perfect blend of historical character and contemporary luxury for those seeking a truly unforgettable San Francisco experience. Only 6 blocks to the new Trader Joe's in Hayes Valley!

description: An enduring classic, this fine historic condo flat is situated on the first floor of a turn of the century Victorian building in the hip neighborhood of NOPA. With high airy ceilings and fine rich oak floors, this beautiful property offers an open and modern living, dining and kitchen area at one end and a private grand suite bedroom at the other. The grand bedroom has a delightful adjoining sitting room (or nursery) and double doors to a luxurious en-suite bath. The entry and handsome hallway corridor offers privacy and space, with 2 additional bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms. The well-appointed kitchen features a marble tiled backsplash with stone-composite counters, and stainless appliances. A common laundry room and deeded storage are at the basement level. 1996 Grove Street offers refined elegant living, showcasing a striking profusion of interior details: Coffered ceilings, stately wainscoting, a deep soaking tub in the primary bath, and a decorative fireplace in the living room.

description: Experience coastal luxury living at its finest at 500 Point Lobos Ave. Nestled in Seal Rock, Outer Richmond neighborhood, this beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath residence offers a unique blend of charm and modern comfort. Newly painted San Francisco Single Family Home with gorgeous hardwood floors, a center patio and double pane windows. Two bedrooms and a full bath, a formal dining room and living room with wood burning fireplace, updated kitchen and breakfast area complete the top floor. The lower level offers a bedroom, family room, office area and an additional bathroom. Enjoy the peek-a-boo ocean views from the bright living room. The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances and a breakfast area. Retreat to the spacious bedrooms and wake up to the sound of the ocean. Step outside to the private outdoor oasis, a perfect place to relax and enjoy the ocean breeze in this serene location yet close to wonderful amenities like Safeway, GG Park, Ocean Beach, Sutro Park, 38 Geary, 5 Fulton, Lincoln Park Golf Course and all the restaurants and shops the Richmond has to offer. Embrace a lifestyle of sophistication, natural beauty, and urban convenience. Discover the allure of 500 Point Lobos Ave, where luxury meets the sea. Contact Ms. San Francisco, your Neighborhood Realtor
